### **What is AI TA?**

#### AI TA is a feature available for mini-projects and projects in CS Discoveries Unit 3 - Interactive Animations and Games. It uses It provides the following:

* #### **Automated Assessment**: Instantly assess student work against Code.org's rubrics.
* #### **Feedback Insights**: Provide targeted, constructive feedback to foster student growth.
* #### **Efficiency Boost**: Reduce administrative workload, freeing up more time for teaching.

### **How can I use AI TA?**

#### AI TA is currently piloting! If you are planning to teach CS Discoveries Unit 3 - Interactive Animations and Games **and** would like to join our pilot, please visit <a href="https://code.org/ai/teaching-assistant" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">this page</a> to sign up.

